sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Provider as Garak Provider<br/>(Remote Adapter)
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines API<br/>HTTPS TLS
    participant Validate as KFP: validate_inputs
    participant Scan as KFP: garak_scan
    participant Parse as KFP: parse_results
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Files as Llama Stack Files API<br/>8321/TCP

    Note over Client,Files: Flow 1: Remote Evaluation (Production)

    Client->>LLS: POST /v1/eval/run<br/>benchmark_id, model
    LLS->>Provider: evaluate_rows()
    Provider->>KFP: Create pipeline run<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KFP-->>Provider: run_id
    Provider-->>LLS: job_id
    LLS-->>Client: job_id

    KFP->>Validate: Step 1: Validate
    Validate->>LLS: Check connectivity<br/>Verify garak installation
    Validate-->>Scan: Validated

    Scan->>vLLM: Adversarial probes<br/>Auth: API Key
    vLLM-->>Scan: LLM responses
    Scan->>Files: Upload report.jsonl<br/>Upload raw results
    Scan-->>Parse: Scan complete

    Parse->>Files: Download report.jsonl
    Parse->>Parse: Generate AVID report<br/>Compute metrics
    Parse->>Files: Upload avid.jsonl<br/>Upload summary HTML

    Client->>LLS: GET /v1/eval/jobs/status
    LLS->>Provider: job_status()
    Provider->>KFP: Check run status
    KFP-->>Provider: status
    Provider-->>LLS: status
    LLS-->>Client: completed

    Client->>LLS: GET /v1/eval/jobs/result
    LLS->>Provider: job_result()
    Provider->>Files: Retrieve results
    Files-->>Provider: scores, metrics
    Provider-->>LLS: EvalResult
    LLS-->>Client: EvalResult (scores, AVID report)

    Note over Client,Files: Flow 2: Inline Evaluation (Development)

    Client->>LLS: POST /v1/eval/run
    LLS->>Provider: evaluate_rows()
    Provider->>Provider: subprocess: garak run
    Provider->>vLLM: Adversarial probes<br/>Auth: API Key
    vLLM-->>Provider: LLM responses
    Provider->>Provider: Parse results in-process
    Provider-->>LLS: EvalResult
    LLS-->>Client: EvalResult

